The taste of the zero sugar NOS is whatever; it is much less caustic than OG
NOS, maybe even a bit bitter. For a zero-sugar I'd choose the OG over this any
day in terms of taste, but the zero sugar bit of this is great. With 200mg of
caffeine in a 16oz can this is a great way to enjoy roughly the taste of NOS
without all its sugar.

